nanoimage (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * CLI: compress, batch, convert, settings commands
  * GUI: egui-based desktop application
  * Support for JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF compression
  * Batch processing with configurable workers
  * Config persistence and import/export

